org.afplib.afplib

Interface LocaleSelector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocaleSelectorImpl

    public interface LocaleSelector
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Locale Selector'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Loc Flgs
    • Lang Code
    • Scrpt Cde
    • Reg Cde
    • Reserved
    • Var Cde

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getLocaleSelector()
